channel.title: Id of a wall?
channel.description:
Hello, Moparscape!
I am coding something new, but now i need the id of a wall! I looked at google,i do "Wall" there come's 200 up.. I checked them all none was good:o So thats why i ask on Moparscape, What is the ID of a wall? Just a regular wall, like what a bank has.
Thanks, I D D S I
**Edit: I Need a wall like this: [img]http://i258.photobucket.com/albums/hh245/JoeySari/wall.jpg[/img]
